Text:
Much lower quality video than the normal 350mb versions.  I am surprised at ettv/eztv because I can usually depend on you with my auto RSS feeds for high quality without resorting to huge files.  PLEASE keep the quality coming.

I believe this is a repost of eztv's file because it's exactly the same.  So this message is for the team who recorded it.

Thank you, ettv, for all of the great stuff I get from you every day!
